articles.title: UK's Sunak raises 'strong concerns' over alleged China spy in parliament - POLITICO Europe
articles.description: British prime minister discusses case with Chinese Premier Li Qiang at G20 summit in India.
articles.content:
NEW DELHI British Prime Minister Rishi Sunak raised very strong concerns with Beijing about China’s alleged interference in the U.K. parliament.
